From Wikipedia, the free encyclopedia




2021 Indian filmFaactoryDirected byFaisal KhanWritten byAmit GuptaFaisal KhanMaryamProduced byAashish Dubey
                   Salim Babu IbrahimMaryamSafaraz SheriffSharad SinghStarringFaisal KhanRajkumar KanojiaRoaleey RyanCinematographyMohsin Khan PathanEdited bySunil YadavMusic byAslam KeyiSalim SenRelease date
3 September 2021 (2021-09-03)
Running time96 minutesCountryIndiaLanguageHindi
''Faactory'' is an Indian  psychological thriller film released on 3 Sep 2021 and written, directed by and starring Faisal Khan. 
This is Faisal Khan's comeback film after six years.[1]


Cast[edit]
Faisal Khan as Yash Kadam
Roaleey Ryan as Natasha
Rajkumar Kanojia as Tommy
Release[edit]
Faactory was released on 03 Sep 2021 India.[2]

Critical reception[edit]
Faactory was not well received by critics.[3]
